OL,5, Former Top Gear presenter James May has
OL,6, said the show's format "needs a        
OL,7, rethink" following the BBC's decision  
OL,8, to rest the series.                    
OL,10,FProduction was paused after host       
OL,11,FFreddie Flintoff was badly injured in  
OL,12,Fan accident while filming last year.   
OL,14,FMay, who hosted the show alongside     
OL,15,FJeremy Clarkson and Richard Hammond,   
OL,16,Fsaid a new approach was needed.        
OL,18,F"My honest view is - I can say this now
OL,19,F- it does need a bit of a rethink," May
OL,20,Ftold the BBC's Today Podcast.          
